{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act34side_level_act34side_st01","storyGroup":"act34side","storySort":1,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BP-ST-1","storyName":"浪潮守望者","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"阿戈尔的城市“弥利亚留姆”主动与陆地取得联系，邀请伊比利亚派遣使节前往深海。为了解决海嗣问题，阿戈尔将开辟一条联通海洋与陆地的航道。与此同时，乌尔比安也出现在了附近的海域。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act34side/level_act34side_st01","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act34side_st01","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"next":1,"characters":["斯卡蒂","歌蕾蒂娅","幽灵鲨","凯尔希","圣徒卡门","艾丽妮","乔迪","？？？","克莱门莎","罗辛南特","乌尔比安","海嗣"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_bg_27_g18_lighthouse_square.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_sea","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":5},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.7","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"3","id":6},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":7},{"type":"subtitle","text":"一个猎人他走上海岸♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":8},{"type":"subtitle","text":"他的家乡在后，他的路在身前♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":9},{"type":"subtitle","text":"父母与儿女都与他失散♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":10},{"type":"subtitle","text":"他的恋人已经葬身大海♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":11},{"type":"subtitle","id":12},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":13},{"type":"subtitle","text":"一个猎人他走上海岸♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":14},{"type":"subtitle","text":"他的家乡在后，徒余哀叹♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":15},{"type":"subtitle","text":"他的路没有尽头♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":16},{"type":"subtitle","text":"他的路浓雾弥漫♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":17},{"type":"subtitle","id":18},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":19},{"type":"dialog","id":20},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":21},{"type":"subtitle","text":"一个猎人他回到海岸♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":22},{"type":"subtitle","text":"他的旅程结束，他的家乡近在眼前♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":23},{"type":"subtitle","text":"旧日的涛声呢喃♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":24},{"type":"subtitle","text":"可他为什么却步♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":25},{"type":"subtitle","text":"又为什么不安♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":26},{"type":"subtitle","id":27},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":28},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":29},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":30},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":31},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$tech_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_sys_tech_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":32,"musicid":0},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"34","text":"好久不见，斯卡蒂。"},"2":{"id":"34","text":"你好啊，斯卡蒂。"}},"values":[],"id":33},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":34,"end":39},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":35},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","duration":"1.5","id":36},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"好久不见，博士。","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"按照约定，来接你的应该是那个脸皮很厚话又多的黎博利，但你好像并不惊讶。","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":40},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":41},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"43","text":"你和极境都是罗德岛的干员。"},"2":{"id":"43","text":"毕竟这里更靠近你的故乡。"}},"values":[],"id":42},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":43,"end":49},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"嗯，也是。","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你比凯尔希估计的晚到了快一个小时。","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"看来就算有圣徒开具的公函，审判庭该有的审查程序还是一样没落。","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"才不到三个月，除了能派上用场的工人外，这里的居民全都迁去了内陆城镇，取而代之的是几个大阵的惩戒军。","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":50},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":51},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"53","text":"他们在紧锣密鼓地筹备着什么。"},"2":{"id":"53","text":"他们看起来非常紧张。"}},"values":[],"id":52},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":53,"end":56},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#9","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"自从一周前，伊比利亚收到了来自阿戈尔的联络，这座被遗忘的小镇就不再安静了。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_char_263_skadi_9.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"遍地的海洋残渣刺激着这些年轻战士的神经，阿戈尔的声音只会加重他们的焦虑。","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_char_263_skadi_9.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":57},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":58},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"60","text":"阿戈尔的行动确实值得关注甚至戒备。"},"2":{"id":"60","text":"远海中的国家突然发声，没人能充耳不闻。"}},"values":[],"id":59},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":60,"end":63},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"沿着雕塑左侧的这条街道过去，走得快一点，十分钟就能看到大海。","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我们待会儿直接前往伊比利亚之眼。","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":64},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":65},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_sea","volume":"0.7","loop":"true","channel":"sea","id":66},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":67},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"喂，博士，你听见海浪了吗？","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":70},{"type":"text","text":"斯卡蒂微微侧过了头，迎向海风吹来的方向，她的长发在风中舞动，与眼中的阴翳同色。","id":71},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#4","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"浪的层次变得很复杂，我还听见了——星空流动的声音，永不停歇的自然的歌，还有，不被理解的语言......","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_char_263_skadi_4.png"},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"sea","fadetime":"3","id":74},{"type":"dialog","id":75},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":76},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":77},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2.5","block":"true","id":78},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":79,"musicid":1},{"type":"sticker","id":80,"text":"Ishar-mla。","x":"320","y":"340","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","duration":"1"},{"type":"sticker","id":81,"duration":"1","block":"false"},{"type":"delay","time":"1.1","id":82},{"type":"sticker","id":83,"text":"我在。","x":"320","y":"340","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","duration":"1"},{"type":"sticker","id":84,"duration":"1","block":"false"},{"type":"delay","time":"1.1","id":85},{"type":"sticker","id":86,"text":"我们遭受的苦永在。","x":"320","y":"340","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","duration":"1"},{"type":"sticker","id":87,"duration":"1","block":"false"},{"type":"delay","time":"1.1","id":88},{"type":"sticker","id":89,"text":"我们渴望的生永在。","x":"320","y":"340","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","duration":"1"},{"type":"sticker","id":90,"duration":"1","block":"false"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":91},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":92},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#7","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_char_263_skadi_7.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":95},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":96},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$tech_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_sys_tech_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":97,"musicid":2},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"99","text":"斯卡蒂，你还好吗？"},"2":{"id":"99","text":"和家乡恢复联系，反而让你心神不宁？"}},"values":[],"id":98},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":99,"end":104},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"近乡情怯吧......算了，这种感受很难总结。","id":101,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"也可能只是没睡好觉，上次回了一趟海里，好像鲨鱼把她的梦都转移给我了一样。","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"说起来，凯尔希医生为什么这么着急地叫你过来？","id":103,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我不记得你接触过海洋，博士。","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":105},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":106},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"108","text":"不一定，但我记不清了。"},"2":{"id":"108","text":"但似乎，并不陌生。"}},"values":[],"id":107},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":108,"end":114},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"这个回答很模糊。","id":110,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"好吧，我忘了你的情况。这个回答其实很正常。","id":111,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"算了，凯尔希医生把你叫过来，总有她的原因。","id":113,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"走吧，天快要黑下来了。","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":115},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":116},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":117},{"type":"dialog","id":118},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":119},{"type":"charslot","id":120},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":121},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_bg_27_g24_cloudy_sea.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":122},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":123},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":124},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_jump_water","volume":"1","id":125},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","posfrom":"0,-100","posto":"0,0","duration":"1","id":126},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":127},{"type":"effect","name":"$e_shuihua","layer":"1","y":"-350","id":128},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"15","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":129},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","posfrom":"0,-100","posto":"0,0","duration":"1","id":130},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":131},{"type":"charslot","id":132},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":133},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":134},{"type":"charslot","id":135},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":136},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"先别靠过来，等我把水甩干。","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"呀，医生。很少有人能锁定深海猎人的行踪。剑鱼提前告诉你我们要从这儿上岸吗？","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":141},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"极境在这一片海域布置了信息采集装置，目前已经完成校准，与伊比利亚之眼的中控系统直接联通。","id":143,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":144},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"r","id":145},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"这么短的时间，架设一套针对水下环境的定位系统，那个黎博利还挺有能耐的。","id":147,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我应该理解为，罗德岛与审判庭加深了合作？","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":150},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"一周前，水下的那座城市通过特殊频段告知伊比利亚，阿戈尔将开辟一条联通阿戈尔本境与陆地的“航道”。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"然而面对这项庞大的计划，除了大灯塔的定位系统，伊比利亚几乎没有其他获取情报的途径。","id":153,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"显然，作为总战争设计师的您，对此也毫不知情。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":155},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":156},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"鲨鱼，告诉凯尔希我们的发现。","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#13$1","focus":"r","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"这是我和队长第三次潜回斯图提斐拉沉没的地方，距离上一次，仅仅相隔了十天。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"第一次的时候，还能看见爆炸后残存的船体插在海床上，借着从海面透下的微光，舱体内部的金色像是晕开的颜料。","id":161,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"而这一次，巨大的金属船体结构已经完全消失，取而代之的是一片生机盎然的珊瑚丛。","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"......我习惯了做梦，但依然觉得不真实。","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"那块悼亡文明与历史的碑，只树立了极短的时间。","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"“愚人号”已经彻底变成了海洋的一部分。","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"准确说，化作了海嗣巢穴的一部分。","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":169},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#14$1","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"海嗣同化环境的速度加快了。","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3d/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":172},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":173},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"快了很多。","id":175,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"但还有更值得关注的事情。我们的确发现了战争的痕迹，而且就发生在不久前。","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"完全净空，连海雪也不见一丝的海域；扭曲破碎，明显被微型奇点撕扯过的海床......","id":177,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":178},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"能做到这些的，恐怕只有阿戈尔正规军团的舰队。","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":181},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":182},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"作为一个常在陆地上行走的人，凯尔希，你对阿戈尔的关注与了解超乎寻常。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":185},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"虽然远隔无垠的海水，但阿戈尔依然属于泰拉。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":188},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"r","id":189},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1","focus":"r","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"我和歌蕾蒂娅已经决定，前往那座城市。","id":191,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":192},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这无疑是一个冒险的决定。","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":195},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"r","id":196},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"是有一点冒险啦。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"相当冒险。","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"所以，深海猎人已经观察了很久。","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"在那次行动之前，我作为深海猎人总战争设计师参加了科学院与技术院的军事会议。","id":202,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"在两院当时制定的战争预案里，并不存在一座靠近陆地的军事要塞，也不存在涉及“航道”的计划。","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","focus":"l","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"毫无疑问，阿戈尔经历了重大变故。","id":205,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"斩杀伊莎玛拉之后，我们和本境的联系彻底断绝。根据已知的情报很难拼凑出真相。","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":207},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这并不能构成你们重返阿戈尔的充足理由。最先劝阻你们的人甚至并不是我，而是你们旧日的同僚。","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":210},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","focus":"l","id":211},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"你是说......乌尔比安？","id":213,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"乌尔比安也一定明白，陆地上不会有答案。我们必须回到海洋之中。","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"如果刻意与阿戈尔保持距离是他的策略，那我们就更有必要以正式的姿态回归阿戈尔。","id":215,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"......自我从睡梦中清醒以来，海浪时刻在诉说着，迷途的人该回家。","id":217,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#13$1","focus":"r","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"深海猎人，必须返回故乡。","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":220},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我能理解。","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"歌蕾蒂娅，我会与你们同行。","id":223,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"对你而言，这的确是个不可多得的机会。","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":226},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我此行并不仅仅代表我自己，甚至不仅仅代表罗德岛。","id":228,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"伊比利亚？他们往你已经不堪重负的肩膀上多加了一副担子？","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这同样是我自己的选择。","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"罗德岛与伊比利亚审判庭的合作刚刚起步，正如我们之间的合作也依然只是开始。","id":233,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"n","id":234},{"type":"text","text":"凯尔希凝视着歌蕾蒂娅，海风没有吹皱对方那张毫无表情的脸。","id":235},{"type":"text","text":"短暂的沉默后，歌蕾蒂娅点了点头。","id":236},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":237},{"type":"dialog","id":238},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":239},{"type":"charslot","id":240},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":241},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_sea","volume":"0.6","loop":"true","channel":"sea","id":242},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_bg_27_g19_lighthouse_front.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":243},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":244},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":245,"musicid":3},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":246},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":247},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":248},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":249},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"艾丽妮，距离我们收到阿戈尔的联络已经有几天了？","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"八天了，圣徒阁下。","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"这八天里，除了必要的布置、会议和休息时间，您一直站在这里观察着海洋。","id":254,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"阿戈尔一方并未给出明确的接洽时间，我理解您担心错过他们的动向，但......","id":255,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"艾丽妮，看看眼前的海。","id":257,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/da/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":258},{"type":"text","text":"难以辨明颜色的深沉海洋涌动着。或许是海面太过辽阔，天空便显得低沉。","id":259},{"type":"text","text":"海水撞击礁石，激起几米高的浪涛，在这狭小的天地间激荡出轰然声响。","id":260},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"sea","fadetime":"3","id":261},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":262},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"对伊比利亚来说，没有翻涌着恐鱼血肉的海洋，哪怕再喧嚣，也是仁慈的。","id":264,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"我的一位故友，曾是港都最富才情的诗人。","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"宏伟的港都沉入静谧之后，他挣扎着一路向北逃亡，踏着遍地饿殍来到了内陆深处，那座日后将会成为首都的小城。","id":267,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"我看到他在破落的城门前跪下，不住地哀哭。那座城市就从哭声中得到了新的名字，佩尔多尼朵拉，“宽恕已去”。","id":269,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"不过，当时的人们需要的不是哀悼，而是抚慰。许多人更习惯将那个名字简称为佩尔多尼——“宽恕”。","id":271,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"如今，黄金时代的遗产，最后的伊比利亚之眼重新亮起，艾丽妮，这意味着什么？","id":272,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"希望和决心。","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"“希望和决心”，当然。","id":276,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"年轻人，你回答我时的眼神要比达里奥年轻时更加坚毅，这很好。","id":278,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2b/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"但这种鼓舞人心的发言往往并不是最准确的答案。","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"半个世纪后，我们一再后撤的防线终于重新向前推进至此。很快，这里将会成为审判庭新的中枢。","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"可与此同时，我们也将一切袒露在了海洋——海嗣，还有阿戈尔——面前。","id":282,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"伊比利亚已捉襟见肘。这个国家无法再掩藏它长久以来的疲弱和困病，这是不争的事实。","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"而另一个事实是，我们已不可能再次退却。","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":286},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":287},{"type":"charslot","id":288},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":289},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":290},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":291},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"老师——欸，艾丽妮阁下，好久不见。","id":293,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"好久不见。","id":295,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"这一身还挺适合你的。","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#11$1","id":297},{"type":"multiline","name":"乔迪","text":"谢、谢谢。","id":298},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#2$1","id":299},{"type":"multiline","name":"乔迪","text":"啊对了，紧急情况——灯塔刚刚监测到了一批来历不明的信号。","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"信号来源似乎不是海底，而是天空。","id":301,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"乔迪，我想它已经肉眼可见了......","id":303,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":304},{"type":"text","text":"卡门和艾丽妮紧紧盯着远处的天空。年轻的书记顺着两人的视线看过去。","id":305},{"type":"text","text":"他愣在原地。","id":306},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":307},{"type":"dialog","id":308},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":309},{"type":"charslot","id":310},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":311},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_51_i01_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","y":"30","id":312},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","yTo":"0","duration":"20","block":"false","id":313},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":314},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_faceoff_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":315,"musicid":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":316},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bionicuavs","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":317},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.7","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":318},{"type":"text","text":"他们看见了飞翔的鳞群。","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"那是？","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"仿生无人机。早年岛民带上岸的器物里，曾有过类似的造物。","id":321},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":322},{"type":"text","text":"无人机矩阵眨眼间便已越过海面，与高耸的大灯塔遥相对应。其中一只脱离编队，缓缓悬停在三人的面前。","id":323},{"type":"text","text":"机翼如鳍翕动，光的微粒在虚空中舞蹈，亲切而富有磁性的女声旋即响起。","id":324},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bionicuavs_tech","id":325},{"type":"dialog","id":326},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/76/Avg_51_i01_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","id":327},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（伊比利亚语）伊比利亚的诸位，请不必紧张。","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"这是来自阿戈尔的致意。","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我是本国社会行政监察所的技术执政官之一，克莱门莎。","id":331},{"type":"text","text":"卡门端举提灯，平静地直视着身前的无人机。","id":332},{"type":"text","text":"两种截然不同的光亮，仿佛两个截然不同的文明的对话——或者对峙。","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"伊比利亚审判庭，圣徒卡门·伊·伊比利亚。","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"我想，这应当是我们两国之间的首次正式交流。","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"是这样没错。","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"您的伊比利亚语很标准。","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"离开本境前，我为自己录入过伊比利亚的语言模块。如果我的表达有不得当的地方，还请您理解。","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"此外，也请原谅我暂时只能以这种形式与您沟通，伊比利亚......阁下。","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"我们对这种形式的交流没有异议，但我对它发生得如此之迟感到遗憾，执政官阁下。","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"被你们称为“航道”的计划据称已经进行到后半，而近在咫尺的伊比利亚仍对种种细节一无所知。","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"所以我们将迎接伊比利亚的使节前往我们的城市，阿戈尔尊重伊比利亚在被海嗣危机波及时所做出的努力。","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"“波及”——伊比利亚所面对的，只是危机的余波？","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"是的。","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"不必纠结外交辞令，阁下。","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"我们都认同语言的力量。而您的姓名，卡门·伊·伊比利亚，本身便已是一种象征，勇气与魄力的象征。","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"所以阿戈尔才会来此。我们希望达成与伊比利亚、与陆上诸国的合作，开辟一条直抵陆地的航道。","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"我们将净空从阿戈尔本境到陆地之间的大片海域，以便阿戈尔的主力抵达海岸。","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"......我想我不必提醒您，将大量军队派遣至其他国家的边境，这种行为在陆上意味着什么。","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"意味着为了对抗即将到来的巨大威胁，我们将竭尽所能。","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"如有必要，我愿意前往陆地与您会晤，向您详细解释一切。但来到深海，会方便诸位更好地理解我们当下的处境。","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"第八与第十军团的舰队正在有序清剿沿途海嗣。他们随后将迎接诸位前往我们的城市，弥利亚留姆。","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"无人机编队将持续向诸位同步战斗进程与环境变化，直到诸位安全抵达。","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"海洋或许正在酝酿一场前所未有的灾难。","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"而审判官阁下，我忧心大地即使再浩瀚，也不过是另一座孤岛。","id":355},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":356},{"type":"dialog","id":357},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":358},{"type":"charslot","id":359},{"type":"image","id":360},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":361},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_bg_27_g19_lighthouse_front.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":362},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":364},{"type":"text","text":"无人机矩阵收敛了辉光，这场突如其来的通讯已经结束。","id":365},{"type":"text","text":"海风依旧在吹，老人缓缓放下了手中的提灯。","id":366},{"type":"dialog","id":367},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$ponder_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_ponder_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":368,"musicid":5},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","duration":"0.5","id":369},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"“直抵陆地的航道”——她的表达很得体，但......","id":371,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":372},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"阿戈尔无疑是傲慢的。","id":373,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"一个手持利器的傲慢的大人，不屑于对赤手空拳的孩子耍弄心机与手腕。","id":374,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"艾丽妮，将刚刚的通讯内容同步给我们的合作伙伴。","id":375,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"凯尔希已经同意作为伊比利亚的使节出访阿戈尔，一直对航道计划心存疑虑的深海猎人此时应该也已经做出了决定。","id":376,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"是！","id":378,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"我也会尽快与格兰法洛的其他审判官将事务交接清楚。","id":379,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":380},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":381},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":382},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":383},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":384},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":385},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":386},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"老师，刚才与阿戈尔通讯的全部内容，我都做了记录，请您过目。","id":388,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"您、您是否批准我前往......","id":390,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8e/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"书记，一周前你就已经提交了申请。","id":392,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"是的，既然现在阿戈尔的舰队马上就要来了，我想，是不是......","id":394,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8e/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"如果已经做了决定，犹豫反而会让你的表态没有说服力。","id":396,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我很小的时候，蒂亚戈叔叔就总是忧心忡忡的。他跟我说：“乔迪，你应该离开格兰法洛，离开伊比利亚。”","id":398,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"可他没法告诉我，我该去哪里。","id":400,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ab/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"阿戈尔，那是我的家乡，我的家乡在大海里，而大海无法靠近。我从没听过阿戈尔的声音，也从没看过阿戈尔的模样。","id":402,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"但现在，它很近。","id":404,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":405},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"审判庭同意你的申请，乔迪·方塔纳罗萨。你将作为伊比利亚的使节，与艾丽妮和凯尔希一同前往阿戈尔的城市。","id":406,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":407},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"谢谢您。","id":408,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8e/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"不。这并不是一次奖励，你在审判庭的工作做得算不上好。","id":410,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"选择艾丽妮，是因为她已经做好了准备，甚至为此抛弃了自己坚持许久的信念。","id":411,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"而选择你，恰恰是因为你仍然困惑和怅然，软弱终究会腐蚀你。","id":412,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"加入审判庭是一次考验，回到自己的家乡，同样也是一次考验。","id":413,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我、我明白的，老师。","id":415,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":416},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":417},{"type":"charslot","id":418},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":419},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_bg_51_g12_seabed.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":420},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":421},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":422},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_463_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":423},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":424},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_horse","id":425},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗辛南特","text":"（兴奋的嘶鸣）","id":426,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_463_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":427},{"type":"charslot","id":428},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":429},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":430},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"——","id":431},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":432},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"这里已经是海沟的最深处。","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"它们掏空了海沟两侧的峭壁，向内筑巢。所以我们绕了好几圈，都没有发现这里。","id":434},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_463_1#1$1","id":435},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_horse","id":436},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗辛南特","text":"（警惕的嘶鸣）","id":437,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_463_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"嗯。我也闻到了。","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"这种气味......海嗣在摧毁了原有的海洋生态之后，又创建了一套完全只为它们自己服务的生态系统。","id":440},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"如此完善的海嗣生态系统，原本只存在于海洋的深处。","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"回去吧，罗辛南特。接下来我一个人进去。","id":442},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_463_1#1$1","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗辛南特","text":"（不悦地晃动脖颈）","id":444,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_463_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":445},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"整块大陆架都在变化，我需要知道，究竟是谁在使海浪鼓噪。","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"告诉骑士，别停止狩猎。","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我们只是暂时分别。","id":448},{"type":"dialog","id":449},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":450},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":451},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_swimdeepsea","id":452},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":453},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_51_i03.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","x":"-20","id":454},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","xTo":"0","duration":"45","block":"false","id":455},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_underwateramb","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":456},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"3","id":457},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"20","block":"false","id":458},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":459},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$chenandwei_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act14d0d0/m_avg_chenandwei_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":460,"musicid":6},{"type":"text","text":"乌尔比安游进了巢穴。","id":461},{"type":"text","text":"他没有选择潜行，因为发光的植物海嗣点亮了巢穴的每一个角落，他无处可藏。","id":462},{"type":"text","text":"在盘旋而上的厚实叶片之间，造型奇特的微小生物在酣眠或游弋。","id":463},{"type":"text","text":"海床原本的岩石已不可见。溟痕缓缓摇动着细小的触肢，捕捉着有机物的碎屑，它们织成层层叠叠的菌毯，淹没了乌尔比安游动的声响。","id":464},{"type":"text","text":"他清晰地感受到自己身体的变化。意识在舒展，躯壳在放松，体内的每一个细胞都在试图回应着什么。","id":465},{"type":"text","text":"他分明是闯入这里的异类，可整个巢穴都在向自己盛开。","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"Ul......Ul-pian......咕......Ul-pianus，同胞。","id":467},{"type":"text","text":"乌尔比安几乎能看穿海嗣接近透明的躯体，他在等待对方吐出捕食或者被他捕食之类的蠢话，但是并没有。","id":468},{"type":"text","text":"海嗣，在思考他的思考。","id":469},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"终于。你走过长路。","id":470},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"这里。营养足够。褪去累赘的血肉。","id":471},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"回归。滋长。迁徙。","id":472},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"哼。","id":473},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"我为你而生，Ul-pianus，只为你而生。","id":474},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"我解开你。疑惑。我引导你。回归族群怀抱。","id":475},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你们因何迁徙？你们要去向何方？","id":476},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"Ul-pianus，你仍动摇。","id":477},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"同胞，你需要知晓大群。你想要知晓大群。","id":478},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"生代即将苏醒。生代需要回归。新的循环。建构海洋。离开海洋。","id":479},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"生代苏醒？离开海洋？","id":480},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"大群。看见。新的长路。我们尽快——","id":481},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......那么，那座城市在进行的事情，与你们有什么关联？","id":482},{"type":"dialog","id":483},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":484},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":485},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":486},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":487},{"type":"image","id":488},{"type":"charslot","id":489}],"characters":["斯卡蒂","歌蕾蒂娅","幽灵鲨","凯尔希","圣徒卡门","艾丽妮","乔迪","？？？","克莱门莎","罗辛南特","乌尔比安","海嗣"]}